The Queue (FIFO) could be optimal for this question 

* Steps : 
		Step 1 : Add all elements in queue (FIFO)
		Step 2 : Create funtions according to Queue data structure


```
class PeekingIterator implements Iterator<Integer>
{
    private Queue<Integer> queue;
	public PeekingIterator(Iterator<Integer> iterator)
    {
	    queue = new LinkedList<>();

		// Adding elements to queue
        convertToQueue(iterator);
	}

	public Integer peek()
    {
        return this.queue.peek();
	}

	@Override
	public Integer next()
    {
	    return this.queue.remove();
	}

	@Override
	public boolean hasNext()
    {
	    return this.queue.size() > 0;
	}

	// Converting Iterator to Queue
    private void convertToQueue(Iterator<Integer> iterator)
    {
        while(iterator.hasNext())
        {
            queue.add(iterator.next());
        }
    }
}
